JXWChanges

"<html>

<head>
<title> Changes from previous versions </title>
</head>

Please send all bug reports and suggestions for features to 
<a href=http://johnlindal.wix.com/aboutme>John Lindal</a>.

<p>
<hr>
<p>

<b>4.0</b>

<p>
Window layouts adapt to translated text widths and font size differences.
<p>

<b>3.0</b>

<p>
Anti-alised text.
<p>

<b>2.5</b>

<p>
No longer copies version control directories when building a project from a template.
<p>

<b>2.1</b>

<p>
Projects can be placed anywhere, not merely in <tt>JX-2.1.0/programs/</tt>.
<p>
Changed file name convention to use _pre_ and _Binary_ instead of &lt;pre&gt; and &lt;Binary&gt;.
<p>
Automatically creates the project directory if it doesn't exist.
<p>
Added library template in <tt>lib_template</tt>.
<p>
Project path and name can now contain spaces.
<p>

<b>2.0</b>

<p>
Initial release."
